{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/extras/LOGO_DeadlyShaft.png?t=1729747555\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">NOTE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>This product is still in a very early alpha phase</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SURVIVE IN THE VILLA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the mansion, you are on your own. You are being held captive by the landlord in the mansion and due to the trauma you suffered during the kidnapping, your magical abilities have been depleted. You are monitored by numerous security cameras in this complex mansion and the landlord has taken away all your items from your inventory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CURRENT FUNCTIONS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Your character starts directly in the villa </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play your character either with the first-person perspective or third-person camera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You can carry a canister </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Day &amp; Night Cycle  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You can sit on benches and survey the landscape </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You can hide in closets </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The householder can chased you if he sees you outside working hours</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> There are security cameras in the mansion to watch you </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> House owner's loyalty is displayed </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SPECIAL FEATURES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/extras/deadly_shaft_2.gif?t=1729747555\" />You can carry items in the mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SET YOURSELF ON BENCH</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/extras/deadly_shaft_3.gif?t=1729747555\" />Also enjoy the beautiful view for a change and take a break from work. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FLY AND HIDE FROM THE HOUSEHOLDER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/extras/deadly_shaft_1.gif?t=1729747555\" />If the landlord notices you, you will be chased by him.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CAMERA SYSTEM</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/extras/Deadly-Shaft_5.gif?t=1729747555\" />You will be seen by numerous cameras in the mansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DAY &amp; NIGHT CYCLE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/extras/deadly_shaft_5.gif?t=1729747555\" />Survive the day, through the day and night change.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PLANNED FUNCTIONS - [COMING SOON]</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Meet mission objectives and duties of the householder.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Hostile environment of the mansion with securitys</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> More hiding and interactive environment options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Locked areas with door code system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Inventory system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Skills or magical abilities (ability attributes)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Open World (Island)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Escape from the mansion (story)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Multiple languages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Steam achievements</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ENABLE YOUR MAGIC SKILLS (PLANNED)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The more you find out knowledge from this landlord, the more you can unlock your magical abilities.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729747555","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729747555","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729747555","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1729747555","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[1,2,5],"notes":"This game may contain content that is not suitable for all ages or for viewing in the workplace: Frequent depiction of mild nudity, violence, blood or mutilation, General adult content."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626150/extras/LOGO_DeadlyShaft.png?t=1729747555\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">NOTE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>This product is still in a very early alpha phase</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SURVIVE IN THE VILLA</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the mansion, you are on your own. You are being held captive by the landlord in the mansion and due to the trauma you suffered during the kidnapping, your magical abilities have been depleted. You are monitored by numerous security cameras in this complex mansion and the landlord has taken away all your items from your inventory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">CURRENT FUNCTIONS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Your character starts directly in the villa </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph